<h2 id="重置-icloud" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#重置-icloud" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 重置 icloud</h2>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 结束 bird 这一 iCloud 文件同步的核心进程</span>
<span class="token function">killall</span> birdkillall cloudd
<span class="token comment"># 结束 cloudd 这一 iCloud 文件同步的核心进程</span>
<span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span> ~/Library/Application<span class="token punctuation">\</span> Support
<span class="token comment"># 将原本 Application Support 文件夹中的 CloudDocs 文件夹重新命名成为 CloudDocsOld</span>
<span class="token function">mv</span> CloudDocs CloudDocsOld
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="一些用过的正则" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#一些用过的正则" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 一些用过的正则</h2>
